---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { getCasos, getCasoImage, getCasoImageAlt } from '../../lib/wp';

const casos = await getCasos('en', 6);
---

<Layout
  title="Brand Experience | CAS Contenidos Advertising"
  description="Faced with new consumer behaviors, experience emerges as the main driver of brand awareness, preference, and loyalty."
>

  <section class="bg-black">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 min-h-screen">
      <div class="min-h-80 lg:min-h-screen bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('/img/experiencia-marca.jpg')"></div>
      <div class="flex items-center px-10 md:px-16 py-20">
        <div>
          <a href="/en/que-hacemos" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-['Inter'] text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-500 hover:text-[#ffb876] transition-colors mb-10">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_back</span>
            What We Do
          </a>
          <h1 class="font-['Space_Grotesk'] font-black text-5xl md:text-6xl tracking-tighter leading-[0.9] text-[#F69220] mb-10">
            Brand<br />Experience
          </h1>
          <div class="space-y-5 font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans'] text-white text-base leading-relaxed mb-12">
            <p>Faced with the new consumer behaviors and the paradigms of traditional communication, experience emerges as the main driver of brand awareness, preference, and loyalty.</p>
            <p>Today it is impossible to think of a Marketing Plan without its experiential component.</p>
            <p>All brands, to a greater or lesser extent, must think about how to approach and interact with consumers—to generate the engagement that leads to future sales and long-term sustainability.</p>
            <p>At CAS, we create and execute those experiences that connect with the consumer, resulting in increased brand positioning.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-400">To achieve objectives in each project, we apply our methodology based on <strong class="text-white">4 key pillars:</strong></p>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            {[
              { key: 'Think.', desc: "Respond to and make evident the brand's purpose—its reason for being." },
              { key: 'Sense.', desc: 'Produce immersive experiences that stimulate all five senses.' },
              { key: 'Feel.',  desc: 'Create an emotional impact.' },
              { key: 'Connect.', desc: 'Generate a sense of belonging and identification with the brand.' },
            ].map(p => (
              <div>
                <p class="font-['Space_Grotesk'] font-black text-[#F69220] text-lg">{p.key}</p>
                <p class="font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans'] text-white text-sm leading-relaxed mt-1">{p.desc}</p>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-[#f5f5f5] py-20 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-8">
      <h2 class="font-['Space_Grotesk'] font-black text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight text-black leading-tight">
        We provide an integral solution covering all stages of the process:
      </h2>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3">
    <div class="bg-[#26c6da] text-white text-center px-10 py-16">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl mb-6 block">lightbulb</span>
      <h3 class="font-['Space_Grotesk'] font-black text-2xl uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Planning</h3>
      <p class="font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans'] leading-relaxed">Strategy and creative proposal for the action.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-[#F69220] text-white text-center px-10 py-16">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl mb-6 block">polyline</span>
      <h3 class="font-['Space_Grotesk'] font-black text-2xl uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Implementation</h3>
      <p class="font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans'] leading-relaxed">Reconnaissance, design, production, installation, and development.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-[#EA2227] text-white text-center px-10 py-16">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl mb-6 block">photo_camera</span>
      <h3 class="font-['Space_Grotesk'] font-black text-2xl uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Control</h3>
      <p class="font-['Plus_Jakarta_Sans'] leading-relaxed">We have a team for control and monitoring of the action across the entire region.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-black py-24">
    <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8">
      <h2 class="font-['Space_Grotesk'] font-black text-5xl md:text-7xl tracking-tight text-white text-center mb-16">
        Success Cases <span class="text-[#F69220]">.</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {casos.map(caso => (
          <a href={`/en/casos/${caso.slug}`} class="group block">
            <div class="relative overflow-hidden aspect-4/3 rounded-2xl mb-4">
              <img alt={getCasoImageAlt(caso)} class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110" src={getCasoImage(caso)} loading="lazy" />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-black/70 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 flex items-end p-6">
                <span class="font-['Space_Grotesk'] font-bold text-white text-sm uppercase tracking-widest">View case</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-['Space_Grotesk'] font-bold text-lg text-white group-hover:text-[#ffb876] transition-colors tracking-tight" set:html={caso.title.rendered} />
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
      <div class="text-center mt-16">
        <a href="/en/casos" class="inline-block border border-white/20 text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] font-black uppercase tracking-widest px-12 py-5 hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all duration-300">View all cases</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
